snippet.title: Widow's Walkabout Launch Trailer- Walkabout Mini Golf
snippet.description:
Local legend says that the spooky old house on the cliff is haunted by a playful spirit who has possessed an eerie mini golf course like no other. #WidowsWalkabout is the mysterious manor you’ve been waiting to sneak into… Step through our doors now!

Available on MetaQuestVR, PlayStation VR2, SteamVR, and PICOxr!
